Storyline

Estranged from her family, Franny returns home when an accident leaves her 
brother comatose. Retracing his life as an aspiring musician, she tracks 
down his favorite musician, James Forester. Against the backdrop of Brooklyn's
music scene, Franny and James develop an unexpected relationship and face 
the realities of their lives.
